post_text:
Tonight we celebrated the 2020 Secondary Educators of the Year at Brennan HS! Congrats to all our #NISDLegends!

Our District winners are-

First Year Middle School Educator of the Year Jasmine Mendiola from Folks MS;

First Year High School Educator of the Year Shane Lemanski from Brandeis HS;

Middle School Educator of the Year Gustavo Trevino from Neff MS;

High School Educator of the Year Jennifer Schulze-Aguirre from Brandeis HS;

and Trinity Prize Nominee Jamie Pfeil from Warren HS!!

